==English==

===Noun===
'''aurochs'''
# {{zoology}} The [[European bison]] (''Bison bonasus'', or ''Europæus'') , once widely distributed, but now nearly extinct, except where protected in the [[Lithuania]]n forests, and perhaps in the [[Caucasus]]. It is distinct from the Urus of Cæsar, with which it has often been confused.

